From: Yelninei <yelninei@tutamail.com>
Date: Sat, 11 Apr 2026 19:42:55 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/4] phobos: Port to GNU/Hurd

---
 libphobos/src/std/datetime/timezone.d | 1 +
 libphobos/src/std/math/algebraic.d    | 1 +
